################## switch mode
Insert Mode
	i
Command Mode
	ESC
################## save, quit in Command Mode
	Speichern ohne Beenden
		:w
	Beenden
		:q
################## Cut/Copy, paste
	1. Position cursor at begin
	2. v to select characters or V to selct whole lines
	3. move cursor to end
	4. y (=yank, means copy) to copy or d (=delete, same as cut) to cut
	5. move to begin of insert
	6. P to paste before cursor or p after cursor
